			"location": "United States",
			"name": "Miles Efron",
			"email": "mefron@illinois.edu"
			}			
		]
	},
	"poster01": {
		"abstract": "This work discusses the consequences of choosing a sample space based on the interpretation of an experiment. We discuss the paradoxes that have been extensively studied in literature, and then we propose an alternative interpretation of the problem of document classification.",
		"title": "More Than Words: A Review of Planets, Stars and Sample Spaces",
		"authors": [
			{
